casebody.data:
Thursday, January 17, 2002

MERIT DOCKET

01-2213. State ex rel. E. Galbraith Nursing Homes, Inc. v. Bowman.

In Prohibition. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of prohibition. Upon determination pursuant to S.Ct.Prae.R. X(5),

IT IS ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.

*1436Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Douglas, J., dissents and would grant an alternative writ.
